	* pbuilder-updatebuildenv: instead of purge lilo,
	purge $REMOVEPACKAGES
	Tried to add something like: -o 'DPkg::Options={"--force-confnew";}' 
	to apt-get dist-upgrade, but it doesn't seem to function.

